Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------main------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方…不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  工作结束了到我家来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是…练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…也没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经睡了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气晴朗  降水率30%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错啊  热柠檬茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我教心怎么沏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真从容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我讨厌有男朋友的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卯月也常说「我教你什么什么」的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的话  心也去找个男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  姐姐变了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方乱来被谁看到了很不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  快迟到了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同学今天也一定在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和爸爸约会时常做的充满回忆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一边感叹着我也到这年龄了一边教我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在还来得及  送上圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊野山间酒店  住一夜要40万哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要去的话  请我去那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  别当真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  怎么搞的  一副没睡醒的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没做两人份的早餐  太累了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脸上粘到什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界今早和伊藤在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说伊藤和4班的桂同学分手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}把我们的事告诉桂同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经不能算是练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话太对不起桂同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  更要早点说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请品尝  还很热哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…不合口味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妈妈说这甜度刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好练习来满足诚君喜欢的口味的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  这个真的很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太好喝了  诚吃惊得说不出话了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  甜度刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也暖和起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:08:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这个其实是妈妈说「能把他一击击倒」的秘传热柠檬茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后要一起去买东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天我妹妹要到家里来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  今天能到你那里去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  但诚你刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹和离婚的爸爸一起住  偶尔回来玩是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又对桂同学撒谎了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的事最后也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  我总有一天会好好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界也这么觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那好像已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
